text: Ulla Petersen (born 27 May 1933) is a Danish equestrian. She competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1933 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Denmark Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Aalborg
